-- B y
-- 2013-01-04T01:10:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-04/japan-banks-toyota-nissan-favored-clsa-s-smith-says-video-.html
Nicholas Smith , a Japan strategist at
CLSA Asia-Pacific Markets Ltd. in Tokyo, talks about the 
country's stock market and his investment strategy.  Japanese stocks advanced, with the benchmark index heading 
toward its highest close since March 2011, as the market resumed
trading following a four-day holiday. Smith speaks with  Susan Li 
on Bloomberg Television's "First Up." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:55
 